---
name: Parse and map an ISC DHCPD message to OCSF DHCP Activity
description: |
  Parses an ISC DHCPD message body and maps the normalized record to OCSF DHCP
  Activity.
---

from {
  time: 2026-01-01T00:00:00Z,
  message: "DHCPACK on 192.0.2.10 to aa:bb:cc:dd:ee:ff (host-1) via eth0",
}
dhcpd::parse
dhcpd::ocsf::map
